data.description: This stately brick home is ready for its new owners. You enter this home in a massive 2 story foyer. With a separate home office space, there is a bonus space for all your needs. There is a large separate dining room for your family dinners. Walking in to your sparkling eat in kitchen, you will find granite counters and all stainless appliances. Cozy up next to the fireplace in your family room, right next to the kitchen! The upstairs has four large bedrooms and two baths. The backyard is fenced in and back deck is waiting to host your next barbecue. If that's not enough room, there is a full unfinished basement, stubbed for a bath. This neighborhood has tennis courts, a pool, and a playground. Come fall in love!
